A regular Summoner's Rift map with a different ban system:

You ban a "Tag" that affects available champions/summoner spells; the following are tag examples:

No Fighter champions  {{champion:24}} {{champion:421}} 

No ADCs ( huuuuge personal favorite ) {{champion:429}} {{champion:85}} {{champion:17}} {{champion:51}} 

No ranged auto attacks {{champion:8}} {{champion:412}} {{champion:6}} 

No mobility {{champion:64}} {{champion:254}} {{champion:38}} 

Mages only {{champion:99}} {{champion:3}} {{champion:30}} 

No male champions {{champion:40}} {{champion:43}} {{champion:222}} 

No ninjas {{champion:238}} {{champion:84}} 

Mana users only {{champion:34}} {{champion:60}} {{champion:121}} 

No smite allowed {{summoner:11}} 

No flash {{summoner:4}} 

Noxus VS Demacia {{champion:122}} {{champion:86}} 

No displacements {{champion:53}} {{champion:412}} {{champion:150}} 

No pushers {{champion:74}} {{champion:15}} 

No limit on champion selection ( you can have 3 {{champion:14}} {{champion:14}} {{champion:14}}  in your team ) 

Certain tags count as mini tags , meaning up to 2 tags can be voted on such as:

No flash , No smite , Mana users only. [ if voted, vote yes/no. If yes, 1 more vote tag ]
